Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,各部门，安全检查中，报告进度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All sections, security check in progress. Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 前部相位炮，正常 - 已驶入标准轨道，护士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Forward phaser, affirmative. - We're entering standard orbit, nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不用太久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Won't be much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,前向传感器接至舰桥…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forward scanner to bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你为何放弃生物研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand you gave up a career in bioresearch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,报名来到星舰的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to sign aboard a starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他还活着，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know he's alive down there, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,后向传感器接至舰桥，情况正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aft scanner to bridge. Status report, green.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎控制…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering controls...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,上次和他通话已是五年前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been five years since his last message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰很坚强，他总能设法活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roger's a very determined man. He'd find a way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,开始与地面通讯，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beginning signals to surface, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,用所有频率传递信号，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put it on all frequencies, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这颗星球的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's record banks show little we don't already know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰的资料库已有详细记录，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about this planet, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可星球地面温度只有零下100摄氏度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the surface temperature of that planet is 100 degrees below zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾经适宜居住，但这片星系的太阳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It may have been inhabited once, but the sun in this system
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去50万年中不断衰退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has been fading steadily for a half-million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再说说科比博士，被大家称为考古医学的奠基人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, Dr. Korby, often called the Pasteur of archaeological medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他翻译了从猎户座废墟挖掘出的医学记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his translation of medical records from the Orion ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的免疫技术因此获得革命性突破\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}revolutionised our immunization techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰学院必修的科目，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Required reading at the Academy, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想见见他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've always wanted to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他还活着吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you think there's any chance of him still being alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所有频率都试过了，长官，没有回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've tried all frequencies, sir. No return signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,接着试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,曲速机能0.07，正在增加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Warp capacity, 0.07 and building.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯官，脉冲引擎甲板需要更多通信线路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communicator, we need more lines to the impulse deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他最后那通信息提到发现地下洞穴的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His last signal told about finding underground caverns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,此后有两支探险队都找过他，但都一无所获\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And since then, two expeditions have failed to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所有频率又试了一遍，舰长，还是没…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've run all frequencies a second time, captain. There's no--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号，请回话，进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise. Come in, Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是罗杰·科比，重复，我是罗杰·科比博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Roger Korby. Repeating, this is Dr. Roger Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了吗，进取号？我是罗杰·科比博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you read me, Enterprise? This is Dr. Roger Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages Of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢地航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
