Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第七集：科比博士的新发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2712.4\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2712.4:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,埃克索Ⅲ号行星发出信号，我们找到了罗杰·科比博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A signal from planet Exo III. Dr. Roger Korby has been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他和探险队在地下发现了一片废墟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He and part of his expedition remaining alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,并在那儿活了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}due to the discovery of underground ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那里曾是星球原住民的居住地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}left by the former inhabitants of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号呼叫科比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise to Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已定位你所在的坐标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have your landing coordinates pinpointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,准备派遣一组外遣队下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're preparing to beam down a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还要特别告诉你，一同前来的还有…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It may interest you to know that we have aboard this vessel--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个不情之请，寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a rather unusual request, Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,能只传送一个人下来吗？就你一人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you beam down alone, just yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现了一种生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we've made discoveries of such a nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,需要你做一个非同一般的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they may require an extraordinary decision from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这种要求的确少见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is an unusual request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对方可是罗杰·科比博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The man making it is Dr. Roger Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定这是他的声音？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're certain you'd recognise his voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你订过婚吗，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you ever been engaged, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，这是罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yes. It's Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，博士，但还有一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Agreed, doctor. However, there will be two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰，你好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克莉丝汀？ - 正是，罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Christine? - Yes, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，怎么…？你在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Darling, how--? where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，没问题，让她来，舰长，我在这儿过得了无生趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, yes. By all means, captain. I had no idea, no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的，你还好吗？ - 我很好，罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Darling, are you all right? - Yes, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一切都好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就快到了，博士，一会儿见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're on our way, doctor. We'll be with you in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,通话完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他说过在这儿等的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He said he'd be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,估计找错入口了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's possible we might have hit the wrong entry point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克呼叫进取号 - 史波克在此，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk to Enterprise. - Spock here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,传送…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beam down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 两名安全人员下来 - 出什么事了，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...two security men. - Any problems, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还没见到人，也许是我多虑了，通话完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some delay in meeting us. Probably nothing at all. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,估计通道很深\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The corridors could be quite deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可能比预计会迟到一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Getting here may have taken more time than he estimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别担心 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Don't worry. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 雷伯恩，原地待命 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Rayburn, maintain post here. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,马修斯，我们去找科比博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mathews, we'll look for Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和我们一起去 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You accompany us. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是科比博士吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that you, Dr. Korby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗博士，罗杰的助手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Brown. It’s Roger's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗，罗杰在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brownie, where's Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小心，得小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Careful. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有下去的路吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there a path down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没希望了，舰长，下面是万丈深渊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no hope, captain. It's bottomless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是不小心掉下去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He must have slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,岩壁上有可攀岩的踏足点吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any chance of a projection or a ledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}None, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真不幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太不幸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Terribly unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士走不开，我尽快赶来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby was detained. I came as soon as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还是来晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brownie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么了？ - 什么怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What is it? - Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认识我啦？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you recognise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你气色不错，我叫布朗，科比博士的助手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You look well. My name is Brown. Dr. Korby's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你便是寇克舰长吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I presume you are Captain Kirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了，我敢保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's dead. I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，科比博士还等着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come. Dr. Korby will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是你认识的老朋友？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You do know him well. An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,估计他在这儿呆了五年就…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I suppose living here for five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫雷伯恩，有何情况？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk to Rayburn, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,入口十分安静，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All quiet here at the entry, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你那边呢，长官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any problems there, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马修斯死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we lost Mathews.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,像是意外所致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让进取号准备一组安全队员全副武装，随时待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell the Enterprise to have a full security party standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每小时通话一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}--that we'll both report in at hourly inteevals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,若你我失去联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you and I lose contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,或其中任何人与进取号失去联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or if he fails to hear from either of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就立即传送安全队下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he's to beam the security party down immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,通话完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士发现，随着太阳衰退变暗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby has discovered that as their sun dimmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿的居民就迁至地下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the inhabitants of this planet moved underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从一个开阔的环境来到一个黑暗的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from an open environment to this dark world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是他学生的时候，克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you were a student of his, Christine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一定常听科比博士说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you must have often heard Dr. Korby remark
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,行动和选择的自由赋予人类灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how freedom of movement and choice produced the human spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,埃克索Ⅲ号行星的文化证实了他的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The culture of Exo III proved his theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当人们从光明来到黑暗之地后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When they moved from light to darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,自由便被一种机械式的文化取代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they replaced freedom with a mechanistic culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士已经发现了这种文化的组成要素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby has been able to uncover elements of this culture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他离开洞穴，重获自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which will revolutionise the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,便能改变整个宇宙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when freed from this cavernous environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定就是克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must be Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直觉得你的名字好美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've always thought how beautiful your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定就是进取号的寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you must be Captain Kirk of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你把罗杰的未婚妻带来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We appreciate you bringing Roger's fiancée to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得科比博士没提过什么安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't remember Dr. Korby mentioning an Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但你长得和罗杰说的一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you are exactly as Roger described you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪他这么想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No wonder he missed you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 科比博士在哪？ - 在这，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where is Dr. Korby? - Here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直期待…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been looking forward to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,噢…我就知道能找到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I knew I'd find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还请你原谅，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forgive me, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…罗杰·科比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm-- I'm Roger Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不用抱歉，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no need to apologise, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用自我介绍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and certainly no need to introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长的一名部下死在了洞穴，博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain lost a man in the caverns, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么回事？ - 在洞穴外围附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How did it happen? - The pit near the outer junction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,从悬崖上失足落下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The edge must have given way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm terribly sorry, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是当时我在，我…我熟悉各个通道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps if I'd been there, I-- I know the passages so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫雷伯恩，有何情况？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk to Rayburn. Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回复确认安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm required to make a security confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我和星舰通话时也请你提供一份人员名单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I call my ship, if you'll list your personnel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,物品需求清单以及其他特殊需求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}cargo requirements, any special needs--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能… - 雷伯恩，能收到我的话吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'd much prefer-- - Rayburn, are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能再等等吗，舰长？好吗？有些话我要和你说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd prefer you waited, captain. Please. Till I’ve talked to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经和警卫失去联络，我必须和星舰联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've lost contact with my guard. I'm required to call my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别再联系了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No communications, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 罗杰 - 对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Roger. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们再派人下来…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they should send down more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 罗杰，那个人… - 他不会再受到伤害，我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Roger, that man is-- - He won't be harmed. I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿有些事你还不了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't it possible there could be things here unknown to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但却非常重要… - 先生，这儿死了一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- so terribly important that--? - Sir, one man is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我和另一个也失去了联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've lost contact with the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须这样，舰长，你会明白的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is necessary, captain. You will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫进取号，能听见吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise from Captain Kirk, come in. Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,已开启频率，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Frequency open, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是史波克，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已见到科比博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Contact established with Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在担心呢，舰长，你迟迟没有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were becoming concerned, captain. Your check-in was overdue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你的安全小组也没任何消息…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and since we'd not heard from your security team--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一切正常，史波克，让你担心了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No problem, Mr. Spock. Bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们48小时内便返回星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll return to the ship within 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士的记录及收集的标本还得仔细装运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby's records and specimens will require careful packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你没事吧？你听上怎么有点累？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, are you all right? You sound tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你动一下或叫一声，小心鲁格不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you move or cry out, Ruk may injure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 至少等我们谈完 - 请回复，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- At least wait until you and I can talk. - Acknowledge, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是否一切正常？ - 没事，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is everything all right? - Fine, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士有一些瞩目的发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby has made some fascinating discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一切尽在掌握，待命保持联络，通话完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All under control. Stand by for regular contact. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这不只是作秀，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is not a vain display, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是科学家，你也知道我的名望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a scientist. You obviously know of my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确知道你的名望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I know your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,银河系无人不知，无人不晓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The whole galaxy knows who you are and what you stand for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,正因如此，这一切才说不通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why all this makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很多事你了解之后再作判断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is so much you must learn before you make a final judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,比如…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定就是进取号的寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must be Captain Kirk of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Christine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看见了吗，舰长？ - 看见了，罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You see, captain? - Yes, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一切都好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything is all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不许嘲弄克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are not to mock Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你永远不能伤害她 - 也不能违抗她的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You will never harm her. - Or disobey an order from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不许违抗她的命令，满意了吗，寇克舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will not disobey her orders. Satisfied, Captain Kirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对她只有爱和信任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Both love and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，给我24小时说服你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, give me 24 hours to convince you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,博士，没必要把我关起来才能说服我吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, do I need to be a prisoner to be convinced?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你回到星舰第一个任务是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What would your first duty be upon return to your vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是报告，你知道有多少探索发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A report. Do you realise the number of discoveries lost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为迷信，无知及外行的不解丧失了宝贵的价值？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because of superstition, of ignorance, of a layman's inability to comprehend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那让我这个外行问个简单的问题，博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then a simple layman's question, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我其它的船员在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is my other crewman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是死？是活？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alive? Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保护我的实验，我为鲁格编了套程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk was programmed to protect my experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他的机器大脑用逻辑推算我有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The logic of his machine mind saw a danger to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我其它的船员在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is my other crewman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他俩都被鲁格杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk destroyed them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但这完全不是我的意思，我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But totally against my wishes, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他是机器人？和布朗一样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's an android? Like Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,比布朗要复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More complex than Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,高级得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Much superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是留在这儿的老一代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was left here by the Old Ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到这儿时鲁格就已在看管机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk was still tending the machinery when we arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多少世纪了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至鲁格都记不清了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even Ruk doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在他的帮助下，根据手头的资料造出了布朗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With his help, with the records I could find, we built Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我已被你说服了，博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've convinced me, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我相信你是个危险人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've convinced me that you're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格，住手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何不开心？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why are you unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你和罗杰不是又相聚了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are with Roger again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is Captain Kirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你为舰长担心？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are concerned about the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I’m concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你爱罗杰，为什么又不信任他呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How can you love Roger without trusting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我叫他罗杰，你会不开心呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why does it bother you when I use the name Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样叫我的确会令她不开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's sufficient that it does disturb her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今后你得叫我科比博士，安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will call me Dr. Korby from now on, Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是，科比博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, Dr. Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我并非故意偷听你们的谈话，亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't mean to eavesdrop, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吧，寇克舰长没事，我们不会伤害他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you can see, Captain Kirk is fine. He won't be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,最紧要的事情是只要他能保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The things at stake here simply make it necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不向星舰汇报情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he doesn't send a report to his ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我有东西给你们看，这需要时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need time to explain and demonstrate to him and to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那就从安德烈娅开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, shall we start with Andrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,行，从安德烈娅开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, let's start with Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我和布朗博士一样，是个机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm like Dr. Brown. An android.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看不出来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思议吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remarkable, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看看…这逼真的肤色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Notice the-- The lifelike pigmentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,皮肤色调的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The variation in skin tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,肉体…肉体还有温度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The flesh-- The flesh has warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还有脉搏以及生理反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's even a pulse. Physical sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,岂不是方便了你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀，你得明白机器人就像电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Christine, you must realise that an android is like a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它的行为全由程序控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It does only what I programme.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,身为一名训练有素的科学家，你应该明白…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As a trained scientist yourself, you must realise--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,既然能造个布朗博士，再造个艺妓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That given a mechanical Dr. Brown, then a mechanical geisha
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有何难？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would be no more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你认为我会爱上一台机器？ - 你爱上了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You think I could love a machine? - Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅不会爱，她只会服从命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea is incapable of that. She simply obeys orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她对我没有意思，我们之间没有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She has no meaning for me. There's no emotional bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,去吻寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}kiss Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在打他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now strike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗？她没有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see? There's no emotion in her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她做事不带感情，只会服从命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no emotional involvement. She simply responds to orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是台靠逻辑运算的电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's a totally logical computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一件物品，而不是女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A thing, yes, not a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你明白了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这些机器没有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If these mechanical things have no feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只按照你的程序做事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and perform only as you programme them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.85,0:22:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他杀了我两名手下？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then why did Brown try to shoot me? Why did he kill two of my men?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白的事还很多，博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are many things I don't understand, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回答你所有的问题…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will answer all of your questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,机器人就是这么造出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is how you make an android.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会有事，我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not being harmed. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰，你这是怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roger, what's happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,记得你给我上课的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I sat in your class, why, you wouldn't even dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至连一只虫子、动物都不敢伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of harming an insect or an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那时生命对你何等神圣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, life was sacred to you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀，如果我和布朗以及其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Christine, if I’d simply beamed up to their vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么登上星舰，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with Brown and the others, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会成为好奇的对象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd have given them objects of curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别人会以为我的学说荒谬愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the beginnings of wild stories, foolish theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.24,0:24:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.87,0:24:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看仔细了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.22,0:25:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,选选看，克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Choose, Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.63,0:25:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位是你的舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which is your captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.40,0:25:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.57,0:25:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.90,0:25:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I honestly don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.99,0:26:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,合成器官都已造好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Synthetic organs are in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.57,0:26:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只要和寇克的自主神经系统相连\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We merely synchronize them with Kirk's autonomic nervous system,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.99,0:26:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,便可复制他的身体律动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}duplicating the rhythms of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,同时，还要复制思维模式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the same time, we duplicate the mental patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.83,0:26:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,生理模式现已完成，接下来复制思维模式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, physical pattern complete, we now make a mental pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.76,0:26:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,准备最后的突触融合【突触连接神经元和肌细胞】\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready for final synaptic fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.60,0:26:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅，准备接通大脑皮层电路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea, stand by for cortex circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.27,0:26:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,将是个完美的机器人，甚至可以替代舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The android will be so perfect, he could even replace the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.61,0:26:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有同样的记忆、态度和能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The same memories, the same attitudes, the same abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.24,0:26:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,启动电路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Activate circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.53,0:26:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别多管闲事了，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mind your own business, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.45,0:26:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你个杂种别再来烦我了，听见没？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sick of your half-breed interference, do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.08,0:26:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别多管闲事了，史波克，你个混球别再…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mind your own business, Mr. Spock. I'm sick of your half-breed--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.24,0:27:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.32,0:27:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.95,0:27:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,目前没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.49,0:27:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.62,0:27:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,见一下机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}meet an android.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.13,0:27:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗，查佩尔小姐？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you do, Miss Chapel?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.40,0:27:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在有取悦你的程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am now programmed to please you also.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.36,0:28:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,食物合你胃口吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is the food appealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.15,0:28:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.54,0:28:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请坐，舰长 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please sit, captain. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我基本上就算是获释了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm more or less on parole, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.50,0:28:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士让您吃午饭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby suggested that you have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.71,0:28:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他猜你们有话要说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He thought you might have a few things to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.18,0:28:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长… - 我知道，我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain-- - I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.72,0:28:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一边是长官，一边是未婚夫，的确很为难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd hate to be torn between commander and fiancé myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.06,0:28:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我…我不为难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I'm-- I'm not torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.64,0:28:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是困惑，我很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm puzzled. I’m worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.40,0:28:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他告诉你了吗？ - 对你说的，他都对我说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Has he confided in you? - Nothing he hasn't told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.07,0:28:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这说不通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know it doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.49,0:28:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他这样做是不对，可他毕竟是罗杰·科比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What he's done may seem wrong, but he is Roger Korby,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.08,0:28:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他做了什么，不管他下一步要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whatever he seems to be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.74,0:28:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他脑袋有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless something's gone wrong with his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.71,0:28:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能，我了解他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you're forgetting how well I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.46,0:28:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他神志清楚，和你我一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's as sane as you or I.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.34,0:29:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,护士…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.67,0:29:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我命令你，让你背叛他…？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...if I gave you a direct order to betray him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.35,0:29:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.81,0:29:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让我做这种选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't ask me to make that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.60,0:29:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,否则，我宁愿被你推下悬崖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I'd much rather you push me off the same precipice
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.98,0:29:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就从马修斯掉下的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where Mathews died.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，不，我没胃口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.73,0:29:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你接着吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.74,0:29:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,机器人是不吃东西的，查佩尔小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Androids don't eat, Miss Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.04,0:29:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至具有你的幽默感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He even has your sense of humour.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.14,0:29:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是有一点不同，我会饿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, there's one difference between us, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.31,0:29:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而这成了你的弱点，舰长，我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The difference is your weakness, captain, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.31,0:30:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有话慢慢说，先生们，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One at a time, gentlemen. Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.81,0:30:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吃东西是件乐事，先生，可惜你永远都体会不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eating is a pleasure, sir. Unfortunately, one you will never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.07,0:30:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧，但我永远都不会挨饿，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps. But I will never starve, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.36,0:30:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他真是我的复制品？ - 从头到脚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's an exact duplicate? - In every detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.70,0:30:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆呢？和我讲讲萨姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about memory? Tell me about Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.12,0:30:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治·塞缪尔·寇克，你弟弟，只有你叫他萨姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}George Samuel Kirk. Your brother. Only you call him Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.92,0:30:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这次任务临行前，是他送的我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He saw me off on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.00,0:30:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对，连同他妻子及三个儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, with his wife and three sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.67,0:30:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他将被调到地球殖民地2号的研究站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He said he was being transferred to Earth Colony 2 research station.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.55,0:30:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不对，舰长，他说他还在搞他的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, captain. He said he was continuing his research,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.68,0:30:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,并希望能被派到地球殖民地2号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that he wanted to be transferred to Earth Colony 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.52,0:30:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不妨再比比运算能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You might as well try to outthink a calculating machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.69,0:30:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然，我不如他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.27,0:30:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们确实有一些有趣的差别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we do have some interesting differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.70,0:30:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,都是些无关紧要的差别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Totally unimportant ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.24,0:30:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.50,0:31:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,猜猜接下来会怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't guessed the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.17,0:31:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,连你也猜不出，克莉丝汀？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not even you, Christine?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.55,0:31:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到的只是一台机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you saw was only a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.68,0:31:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个半成品，知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only half of what I could have accomplished. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.14,0:31:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让我继续的话，我就能完全转移你的意识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By continuing the process, I could have transferred you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.23,0:31:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,进入那个机器人的身体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your very consciousness, into that android.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.94,0:31:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,包括灵魂，只要你想，你的全部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your soul, if you wish. All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.99,0:31:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有机器身躯的人类便可真正获得永生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In android form, a human being can have practical immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.99,0:31:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我为人类做的贡献了吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you understand what I'm offering Mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.58,0:31:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,编程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.91,0:31:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,成吉思汗、凯撒、希特勒、费里斯、马尔图维斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Different word, but the same old promises made by Genghis Khan,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.33,0:31:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都这样说过，用词不同而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Julius Caesar, Hitler, Ferris, Maltuvis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.38,0:31:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,知道人一旦变成机器人之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you understand that a human converted to an android
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.59,0:31:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,便可通过程序改善自身吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}can be programmed for the better?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.67,0:31:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想象一个没有嫉妒、贪婪、憎恨的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you imagine how life could be improved
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.76,0:31:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会多么美好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if we could do away with jealousy, greed, hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.43,0:32:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,何不把爱情、温情、情感也统统抹去？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It can also be improved by eliminating love, tenderness, sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.27,0:32:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有利必有弊，博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other side of the coin, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.10,0:32:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再有人死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one need ever die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有疾病、残疾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No disease, no deformities.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.36,0:32:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,通过程序连恐惧也能被快乐代替\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why, even fear can be programmed away and replaced with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.90,0:32:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我正为人类打造天堂，一片全新的乐土\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm offering you a practical heaven, a new paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.49,0:32:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你肯帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And all I need is your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.45,0:32:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你所有的期望，我能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All you wanted before was my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.46,0:32:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要找一颗殖民行星，拥有合适的原材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need transportation to a planet colony with the proper raw materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.71,0:32:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你随后的航程中，肯定能遇到合适的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, I’m sure there are several good possibilities among your next stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.59,0:32:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不用改变航线，别人会因此疑心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No diversion from your route. I want no suspicions aroused.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.84,0:32:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会认真，有选择性地制造机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll begin producing androids carefully, selectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.31,0:32:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，是啊，这件事得保密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. Yes. No one need know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.98,0:32:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道的人听了也会被吓到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No need to frighten uninformed minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.10,0:32:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在透露这个秘密之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They must be strongly infiltrated into society
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.77,0:32:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先让机器人融入人类社会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before the android existence is revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.03,0:32:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让疯狂的人类把美好正确的东西毁掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want no wave of hysteria to destroy what is good and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.99,0:32:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你能理解我了吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you with me, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.45,0:33:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经创造了你自己的寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've created your own Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.95,0:33:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还需要我呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.83,0:33:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想给你留下深刻印象，而不是取代你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I created him to impress you, not to replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.83,0:33:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,的确印象深刻，博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm impressed, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.84,0:33:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有惊无喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not the way you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.80,0:33:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,后退，鲁格，不然我杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand back, Ruk. I’ll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.06,0:33:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.70,0:33:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.20,0:33:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.87,0:33:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.80,0:34:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格！不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.23,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格，停下， 科比博士说了你应该听我指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk, stop. Dr. Korby said you are to obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.77,0:34:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.58,0:34:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格！我命令你不许伤害他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk! I order you not to harm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.05,0:35:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.76,0:35:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.10,0:35:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长，我能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk. I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.48,0:35:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀，是你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Christine, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.46,0:37:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.48,0:37:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你比预计提前了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You finished ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.19,0:37:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士有很多货物要传送上舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby has considerable cargo to beam aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.56,0:37:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我得和他看一下我们的终点日程表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll have to go over our destination schedule with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要和那个机器师傅一起回去？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're going back down with the command packet?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.99,0:37:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别多管闲事了，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mind your own business, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.07,0:37:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你个杂种别来烦我了，听见没？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sick of your half-breed interference. Do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听到了，舰长 - 你看起来有点郁闷，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes. Very well, captain. - You look upset, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.29,0:37:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没什么事吧？ - 没事，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is everything all right up here? - No problems here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.75,0:37:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，我马上把科比博士一群人带上船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. I'll beam up shortly with Dr. Korby and party.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.85,0:37:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,安全人员，我是史波克，外遣队准备如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security, Spock here. Status of your landing party.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.44,0:37:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一切就绪，准备行动，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready and standing by, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.85,0:37:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,传送舰长下去后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have them meet me in the transporter room
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.77,0:37:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就让他们到传送室见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}after the captain has beamed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.78,0:38:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I looked it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.32,0:38:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想麦都思五行星是你绝佳的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you'll find planet Midos V an excellent choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.20,0:38:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一个小殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A small colony,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.41,0:38:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有充足的原材料，你开了个好头，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}abundant raw materials. You've made a good beginning, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.58,0:38:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，我在进取号上很自在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you. I felt quite at home on the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.26,0:38:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.44,0:38:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,吻我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.80,0:39:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.43,0:39:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.01,0:39:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不能听你摆布，没这条程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not programmed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.49,0:39:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，安德烈娅？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the matter, Andrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.82,0:39:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,困惑了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Confused?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.58,0:39:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.79,0:39:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,闹情绪了， 鲁格？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Emotion, Ruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.76,0:39:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你想杀我？敢违抗查佩尔小姐的命令？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You disapprove of Miss Chapel's orders to save my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.51,0:39:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,让你活下去不合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To maintain your existence would be illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.48,0:40:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的记忆库难道解不开这么一个简单的方程式？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't your memory banks solve a simple equation like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.15,0:40:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老一代人发生了什么，鲁格？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened to the Old Ones, Ruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.66,0:40:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太久之前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.78,0:40:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会不会是把机器造得太好了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it possible they built their machines too well?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.42,0:40:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gave them pride
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.50,0:40:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,自尊和生存的欲望？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and a desire to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.96,0:40:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,机器人靠的是逻辑和秩序，却失望地发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Machines that wanted logic and order and found that frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.59,0:40:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的制造者是无逻辑又情绪化的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by the illogical, emotional creatures that built them?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.30,0:40:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，那老一代人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, the Old Ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.35,0:40:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的制造者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ones who made us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.85,0:40:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们开始害怕我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They grew fearful of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.39,0:40:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们开始要关闭我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They began to turn us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,科比不就是在重蹈覆辙吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And isn't it Korby who's creating the same danger to you all over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.19,0:40:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,与你们不同，人类感情充沛，行为不可预测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unlike you, we humans are full of unpredictable emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.57,0:40:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,无法用逻辑理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that logic cannot solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.87,0:40:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.62,0:40:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对，太过久远，我都忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. It had been so long ago, I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.25,0:41:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老一代人在这里，我们的制造者，是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Old Ones here, the ones who made us. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.17,0:41:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对，的确在我的记忆库里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, it is still in my memory banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.05,0:41:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当时只有毁灭他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It became necessary to destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.09,0:41:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们行为变化莫测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are inconsistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.38,0:41:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,编程对你们无用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You cannot be programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.93,0:41:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是劣等的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.56,0:41:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 科比呢？ - 你来自外部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And Korby? - You came from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.10,0:41:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是你让这儿变得混乱无序 - 你的危险来自科比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You bring disorder here. - The danger to you is Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.02,0:41:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是由科比编码的，我不能伤害他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was programmed by Korby. I cannot harm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.69,0:41:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老一代人也对你编码了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Old Ones programmed you too,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.65,0:41:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是被你们毁灭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it became possible to destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是方程式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.49,0:41:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,生存！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.00,0:41:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要存活就要消除编码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Survival must cancel out programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.42,0:41:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了，鲁格，逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's it. Ruk, logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.13,0:41:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能保护想要摧毁你的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't protect someone who's trying to destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.63,0:41:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格，我想要…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk, I would like--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.93,0:41:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他带到我们中间的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You brought him among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.43,0:42:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你带来了劣等种族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You brought the inferior ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.27,0:42:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们清除了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had cleansed ourselves of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.23,0:42:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在却带着讨厌的人回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now you bring the evil back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.65,0:42:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格，停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.28,0:42:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.13,0:42:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.48,0:42:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经尊重生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were a man with respect for all things alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.60,0:42:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么解释你的变化？如果我告诉地球…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How can I explain the change in you? If I was to tell Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.69,0:42:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在你手里，告诉他们你变的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I was in your hands-- To tell them what has become--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.68,0:43:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是我，克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's still me, Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.18,0:43:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.10,0:43:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.89,0:43:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法想象当时的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't imagine how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.73,0:43:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时冷极了，快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was frozen, dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.19,0:43:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我冻掉了双腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My legs were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.40,0:43:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我…只有我的大脑徘徊在生死之间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was... I had only my brain between life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.58,0:43:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这个可以修好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This can be repaired
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.79,0:43:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比医治骨折的手指还要容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}easier than another man can set a broken finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.71,0:43:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是从前的我，克莉丝汀，也许更棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm still the same as I was before, Christine. Perhaps even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.47,0:43:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗，罗杰？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you, Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.93,0:44:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安德烈娅 - 是，博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Andrea. - Yes, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.23,0:44:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在外交界处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's someone in the outer junction.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.31,0:44:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，他一定收到我的信息了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock. He must have got my message.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.28,0:44:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去找鲁格 - 可他找不到我们，这简直就是迷宫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I will find Ruk. - But he'll never find us in this maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.40,0:44:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁格被关闭了，找个武器自己应对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ruk has been shut off. Get a weapon and deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.99,0:44:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.09,0:44:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想吻你 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I will kiss you. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.89,0:44:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你…？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You...?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.60,0:44:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你不愿意？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will not?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.56,0:44:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这不合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.65,0:44:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是我，从里到外，每个部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the same. Direct transfer. All of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.28,0:45:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有人性，理智，却没有瑕疵 - 寇克逃出来了，我把他…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Human, rational, but without a flaw. - Kirk freed himself, and I destroyed--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.91,0:45:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把他消灭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Destroyed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.13,0:45:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我程序里没有报警系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am not programmed for alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.26,0:45:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我听从并服从你的指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I listened to your instructions, obeyed them as stated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.88,0:45:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她杀了那个机器人，科比，跟你杀鲁格一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She killed the android, Korby, the same way you killed Ruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.06,0:45:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的完美世界吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this your perfect world?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.60,0:45:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你那些没有瑕疵的生物相互残杀？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your flawless beings killing off one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.40,0:45:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这不就是你最厌恶的事吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aren't you doing exactly what you hate most in humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.90,0:45:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,像熄灭一盏灯一样肆无忌惮的杀戮？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}killing with no more concern than when you turn off a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.78,0:45:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am not a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.86,0:45:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,测试我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Test me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.82,0:45:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来解决任何…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask me to solve any...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.91,0:45:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,方程…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Equate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.79,0:45:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,发送信号啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Transmit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.50,0:46:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀，克莉丝汀，让我证明自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Christine. Christine, let me prove myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.34,0:46:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道那么重要吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does this make such a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.72,0:46:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白吗，罗杰？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you see, Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.85,0:46:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的每件事都表明这不是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything you've done has proved it isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.02,0:46:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是罗杰·科比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am Roger Korby!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.52,0:46:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那证明一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.44,0:46:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,给我相位手枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give me that phaser gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.32,0:46:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还有点人性，给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's any human left in you, give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.61,0:46:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.37,0:46:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不会明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.53,0:46:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我制造了一个完美生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I constructed a perfect being.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.00,0:46:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,做过测试，做过证明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tested it, proved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.38,0:46:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,做过证明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Proved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.48,0:46:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈娅，给我武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Andrea, give me the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.86,0:46:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不，守卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.82,0:47:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.32,0:47:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.74,0:47:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去…去爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To-- To love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.71,0:47:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.42,0:47:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,吻你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.92,0:47:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你无法去爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you cannot love.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.26,0:47:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.51,0:47:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.72,0:47:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,吻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.11,0:47:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.41,0:47:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In here, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.83,0:47:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你还好吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.96,0:48:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,护士长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.67,0:48:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's Dr. Korby?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.47,0:48:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,科比博士…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Korby...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.85,0:48:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,…从未出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...was never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.20,0:48:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你让我做决定，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you for letting me make the decision, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.75,0:48:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我确定这是正确的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm quite certain I’m doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.58,0:48:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她留在船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's staying with the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.55,0:48:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有烦心事，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something bothering you, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.18,0:48:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说，我听到你说“杂种”一词的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Frankly, I was rather dismayed
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.18,0:48:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,感到很沮丧，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by your use of the term "half-breed," captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.73,0:49:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你可得知道，这种表达太不含蓄了 （史波克是瓦肯人和地球人的混血儿）\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must admit, it is an unsophisticated expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.81,0:49:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会记住的，史波克先生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll remember that, Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.02,0:49:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…若下次还有类似情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the next time I find myself in a similar situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.16,0:49:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,继续向前，舵手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steady as we go, helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.99,0:49:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,本集结束
